import { createApp } from 'vue'
import Vue from 'vue'
import App from './App.vue'
import Vuetify from 'vuetify'
import 'vuetify/dist/vuetify.min.css'

Vue.config.productionTip = false
Vue.use(Vuetify)

new Vue({
    render: h => h(App),
}).$mount('#app');

createApp(App).use(vuetify).mount('#app')
